lead_paragraph: Manchester City, buoyed by the return of Yaya Toure, will look to seal a spot in the Champions League knockout stage when they travel to Borussia Moenchengladbach on Wednesday to play a team struggling for form.

headline.print_headline: Buoyant City Seek Knockout Spot at Struggling Gladbach
